# Zoom Developer Platform

Stop and verify current Zoom documentation before answering unstable questions about:
- API endpoints and scopes
- SDK versions and platform setup
- MCP tools, scopes, and endpoints
- rate limits
- app types and Marketplace requirements

## Preferred sources

- Zoom API Hub: `https://developers.zoom.us/api-hub/`
- Zoom docs: `https://developers.zoom.us/`
- Zoom Developer Forum: `https://devforum.zoom.us/`
- Zoom MCP:
  - `https://mcp-us.zoom.us/mcp/zoom/streamable`
  - `https://mcp-us.zoom.us/mcp/whiteboard/streamable`

## Routing

Route to the closest matching skill under `skills/` first:
- `skills/general/` for cross-product routing
- `skills/rest-api/` for deterministic API automation
- `skills/meeting-sdk/` for embedded Zoom meetings
- `skills/video-sdk/` for custom video sessions
- `skills/zoom-mcp/` for Zoom-hosted MCP workflows
- `skills/webhooks/` and `skills/websockets/` for event delivery

Do not answer Meeting SDK and Video SDK tasks interchangeably.
Do not answer REST API and MCP tasks interchangeably.
